properties.headline: Tornado Watch issued February 6 at 8:00PM EST until February 7 at 12:00AM EST by NWS Jacksonville FL
properties.description:

FOLLOWING AREAS

IN FLORIDA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 11 COUNTIES

IN NORTHEAST FLORIDA

CLAY                  DUVAL                 FLAGLER
NASSAU                PUTNAM                ST. JOHNS

IN NORTHERN FLORIDA

ALACHUA               BRADFORD              GILCHRIST
MARION                UNION

IN GEORGIA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 2 COUNTIES

IN SOUTHEAST GEORGIA

CAMDEN                GLYNN
